  'Roush Performance': ['Boss F150 Super Cab', 'F150 Pickup', 'F150 Raptor Pickup', 'Stage 3 F-150', 'Stage 3 F-150 Supercab', 'Stage 3 F-150 Supercrew', 'Stage 3 F150 Regular Cab', 'Stage 3 F150 Super Cab', 'Stage 3 F150 Super Crew'],
